    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>This article aims to study the COVID-19 data for New York City. We use both the daily number of second does vaccination and the daily number of reported cases for New York City. This article provides a method to combine an epidemic model and such data. We explore the influence of vaccine efficacy on our results.</jats:p>",
